tags.description: Highway is paved on the Ilocos Norte side but pavement ends near Apayao border then is very rough mix of mud, gravel & large rocks. The Apayao portion of the road is appropriate for hiking but not recommended for driving.
tags.name: Ilocos Norte-Abra Road
